author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Stockland Corporation HY Revenue From Ordinary Activities Up 14.3 Pct
text:
Feb 21 (Reuters) - Stockland Corporation Ltd:
* HY REVENUE FROM ORDINARY ACTIVITIES UP 14.3% TO $1,337 MILLION
* HY NET PROFIT AFTER TAX ATTRIBUTABLE TO SECURITYHOLDERS DOWN 2.6% TO $684 MILLION
* HY FUNDS FROM OPERATIONS ATTRIBUTABLE TO SECURITYHOLDERS UP 18.2% TO $436 MILLION
* HY FFO PER SECURITY WAS 18.0 CENTS * DIVIDEND AND DISTRIBUTION PAYABLE FOR HALF YEAR IS 13.0 CENTS PER SECURITY, WITH A FORECAST FULL YEAR DISTRIBUTION OF 26.5 CENTS FOR FY18 Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
